1
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,680
Th-This... this...

2
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:00,000
Why is there a paper effigy here?

3
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,880
Master prepared this yesterday for the ritual

4
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,520
Where is Master Jiang?

5
00:01:04,520 --> 00:01:06,720
My Master ran out yesterday like he'd seen a ghost

6
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,000
And then he vanished

7
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,120
Mayor, this is bad

8
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:11,000
The jar with Li Zhong's remains is gone too

9
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,080
What?

10
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:14,600
Go find it, now, now, hurry!

11
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,320
Yes

12
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:18,680
What do we do?

13
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:22,200
The weather is truly strange today

14
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,480
Sunny one moment, gloomy the next

15
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,000
What do you mean?

16
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:31,600
What's going on?

17
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:44,840
Master Jiang

18
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,280
I survived this disaster

19
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,680
Many thanks, Mr. Zheng

20
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:03,440
From now on, remember to do more good deeds

21
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:05,840
If you swindle again, disaster will strike

22
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,880
Yes

23
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,640
From now on, I will truly reform

24
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:10,800
I'll never deceive anyone again

25
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:15,080
Master Jiang, how were you trapped in the paper effigy?

26
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,760
It's strange, really

27
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,680
Yesterday I met a little talking paper effigy

28
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,360
Then someone knocked me out

29
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,800
When I woke up

30
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,480
I found myself soaking in a tub

31
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:26,320
After that

32
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,040
Oh, right

33
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,680
Then a masked man sewed my mouth shut

34
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,640
It scared me to death

35
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:37,720
Knocked out and soaked in a medicine vat...

36
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:41,280
Could it be that only those who took the herb bath

37
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,320
would suddenly combust?

38
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,560
Earlier, when I went with my brother for treatment

39
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:49,560
I felt something was off about the bath's smell

40
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:51,640
So I secretly dabbed some with a handkerchief

41
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,040
After taking it home

42
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,760
I compared many medical texts and herbs

43
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:57,320
Still no source for that smell, yet it existed

44
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:02,160
But I did see it sitting there

45
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,480
when it suddenly burst into flames

46
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:08,120
Western Regions Poison Powder. The killer used it

47
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:12,080
This poison powder takes many steps to refine

48
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:16,120
Under sunlight, it triggers spontaneous combustion

49
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:19,960
So those paper effigies could, without any interference

50
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,800
ignite on their own

51
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,920
Then who did it?

52
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:30,960
Where is Xiao Shen?

53
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:34,160
Say, you were almost dead, as his Master

54
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:36,760
How is he not worried at all?

55
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,480
Exactly

56
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,680
That heartless wretch

57
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,760
I must have been blind back then

58
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:46,080
to spend one silver dollar on that ingrate

59
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,200
You bought him?

60
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,280
Yes

61
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,560
Twelve years ago, the plague had just ended

62
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,520
and then famine broke out

63
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,200
To stay alive, many parents

64
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,400
sold their children away

65
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,640
At the time, his father had just died

66
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:01,240
His mother truly couldn't keep him alive

67
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,600
So she sold him to me

68
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,520
Zheng Yu

69
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,560
Don't come over

70
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,960
I'm covered in poison powder

71
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,280
Don't come over

72
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,680
Get out

73
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:10,640
Get out

74
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,440
Xu Nan, leave me alone

75
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,280
Hurry and get out

76
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,480
Are you crazy?

77
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,280
You actually went after the killer alone

78
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,400
Do you know you nearly lost your life?

79
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,400
Ow

80
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,120
What is it?

81
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:32,320
Where does it hurt? Did I hurt you?

82
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,880
My heart aches

83
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,440
I thought

84
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:50,600
I'd never see you again

85
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:57,520
Oh, right

86
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:01,120
The ointment I made can remove the poison powder

87
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:03,840
Apply some of it

88
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:08,480
Can you bear to make an injured man do it himself?

89
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:19,560
I know where Xiao Shen is

90
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,440
Help!

91
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,480
Help! Mr. Zheng, don't come over

92
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,880
You're actually not dead

93
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,880
Xiao Shen, have you gone mad

94
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:28,240
What are you trying to do

95
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,080
You're Li Zhong's son, aren't you

96
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:33,640
What? Li Zhong's son?

97
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,880
All the victims in the paper effigy case

98
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:38,040
were those who burned Li Zhong to death

99
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:40,960
The killer must be closely tied to Li Zhong

100
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,160
That day, when we gathered Li Zhong's bones

101
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,680
you were unusually attentive

102
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,680
Later, we met at the noodle shop

103
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:50,360
You seemed grateful I treated Li Zhong kindly

104
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,200
At the time, I only found it strange

105
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,120
but I didn't think much of it

106
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,800
Not until yesterday, when your Master said

107
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,640
he bought you 12 years ago

108
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,880
did I finally connect it all

109
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:05,520
I suppose you stole his remains too

110
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,720
You're right

111
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,520
But it's already too late

112
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:11,320
I could kill him right now

113
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:14,680
But stabbing you once is too easy on you

114
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:17,520
I'll let you taste being burned alive too

115
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,920
Your father trafficked girls and enraged all

116
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,480
Being burned to death was what he deserved

117
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,840
Yet you've slaughtered innocent people

118
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:24,200
and got my brother killed

119
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:26,280
My father was no trafficker

120
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,880
He was the Shaman Divine Doctor who saved Nanwan Town

121
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:35,120
Back then, when plague struck Nanwan Town

122
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,760
everyone was helpless

123
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,880
until my father appeared

124
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:43,480
To save more of the sick

125
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:46,680
he risked his life every day

126
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:50,960
digging plague-curing herbs from sheer cliffs

127
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:54,800
And to keep the plague from spreading too fast

128
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,480
he spared no effort

129
00:07:57,840 --> 00:08:00,600
treating the townsfolk day and night

130
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,760
It was thanks to my father

131
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:05,280
that Nanwan Town survived that plague

132
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:08,160
Burn him to death? But these jerks

133
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,440
for the sake of their own gain

134
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,880
framed my father for trafficking girls

135
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:15,560
then burned him alive

136
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:18,040
He deserved to be burned to death

137
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,640
And your brother too

138
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,480
he was no good either

139
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:27,400
He had a hand in my father's burning too

140
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,120
Is everything he said true

141
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:34,360
To cover up the truth

142
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,560
they made my father the scapegoat

143
00:08:37,800 --> 00:08:39,680
Tell me, should these jerks be killed

144
00:08:39,680 --> 00:08:40,800
Careful, careful, Xiao Shen

145
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:41,840
Don't act rashly yet

146
00:08:42,040 --> 00:08:43,320
If they are guilty

147
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,040
someone will surely punish them

148
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,200
Put the knife down first

149
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,560
Really?

150
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:50,320
A full 12 years

151
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,720
I've endured hunger and starvation

152
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,200
and suffered endless humiliation

153
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,720
Look at them

154
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,880
lofty and untouchable

155
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:58,120
living in silk and luxury

156
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:01,280
This is the justice and righteousness you speak of?

157
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,720
It's nothing but a joke

158
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,160
Careful. Go!

159
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:09,720
Go!

160
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,040
Go!

161
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:14,520
Go!

162
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,400
Stop now, Xiao Shen

163
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,560
Go see your dead damned father

164
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,760
You want my life?

165
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:31,520
You're still too green

166
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:33,040
Go to hell

167
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:53,680
Burn him to death! Burn him to death!

168
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,560
Who would have thought behind this strange case

169
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:24,680
there was such a human tragedy hidden

170
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:29,280
The ugliness of human nature cannot face the light
